<p>
	Sweet Viola is a Tales of Avalon fairy designed by Lisa Parker. This fairy is made from resin and finished with beautiful colours. The fairy is sitting on rocks with flowers resting on and around her legs. She has one leg bent with her knee up against her chest, resting her hand gently upon it. She is wearing a long, flowing burgundy dress with knee high stockings and fabric covering her arms. Her stunning features are created with&nbsp;great detail and her wings are spread and bright on her back.&nbsp;This fairy comes packaged in a decorative gift box making her a perfect gift for a fairy lover. She measures 19cm tall and 13cm wide.</p>
